VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT @require_(GET|POST)[\s\S]*?def\s+(\w+)\(.*?request.*?:
WHEN EXPR MISSING:cleaned_data|validate|sanitize|escape
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects instances where either the require_GET or require_POST decorator is used and the request object is accessed in the view function.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Untrusted Inputs: Request Usage with require_GET or require_POST Decorator.
